  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13068830/inghams-special-offers-ski-holidays.jpg" alt="Exclusive Special Offers" data-udi="umb://media/8f0108541778428b9a4a1ee49670b898" /><br />It's not just about great value ski holidays - with our exclusive special offers you can get great value on a range of goods and services from our trusted partners.</div>
<div> </div>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Book your winter holiday with us to receive the following outstanding benefits:</h3>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p align="center"><img style="width: 321px; height: 182px;" src="/media/13089480/eco-ski-800x445.jpg?width=321&amp;height=182&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a8046dafacbf4de19a921aadf2672651" /></p>
<p> </p>
<h3>15% off rental and 5% off new at Eco Ski </h3>
<p>Eco Ski is a unique rental retail platform that sells and re-purposes environmentally friendly gear, allowing skiers and snowboarders to look and ride their best this winter without breaking the bank or the Earth. Buying or rent your next seasons look through EcoSki means you'll not only stay trendy but you will also be doing your bit for the planet, to help ensure our mountains don't lose their snow. </p>
<p><strong>Receive a 15% off rental and 5% off new clothing when you book your ski holiday with Inghams. </strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a rel="noopener" href="https://ecoski.co.uk/" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Visit the Eco Ski</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p align="center"><img src="/media/13098825/crevasse2.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/045f7e7677b2403aa2cf7afa132f9cd5" /></p>
<h3>10% discount Crevasse Clothing</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;" align="center">Crevasse Clothing have been providing up to date, stylish ski and snowboard clothing to customers for the last 15 years. The Full Rental Package includes jacket, pants, goggles and gloves plus a free pair of socks. Why spend a small fortune on items that you will use once a year, when you can rent your gear, hassle free? Rest assured that they choose the best brands so that you will fully enjoy winter holiday in comfort and style whilst also being sustainable.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><strong>Get a 10% discount code when you book your ski holiday with Inghams.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.crevasseclothing.com/" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Visit Crevasse clothing<br /></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p align="center"><a href="https://www.aph.com/?campaign_code=GAPH101&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIw-yQsu_L3QIVyed3Ch2V-QpIEAAYASAAEgKtxfD_BwE" title="aph.com" data-anchor="?campaign_code=GAPH101&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIw-yQsu_L3QIVyed3Ch2V-QpIEAAYASAAEgKtxfD_BwE"><img src="/media/13070433/inghams-special-offers-with-aph.jpg" alt="35% with Inghams on APH airport car parking" data-udi="umb://media/f5cca846ec4d4ded8f30883721974b41" /></a></p>
<h3>Up to 35% discount with APH</h3>
<p>We've teamed up with APH to provide our guests with excellent rates on airport services including airport car parking, hotels and lounges.</p>
<p><strong>Pre-book with APH and save up to 35% on the cost of your airport parking.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.aph.com/?campaign_code=GAPH101&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIw-yQsu_L3QIVyed3Ch2V-QpIEAAYASAAEgKtxfD_BwE" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Visit APH Parking</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Terms and Conditions</h3>
<p>*Full Terms and Conditions apply</p>
<p>Not to be used in conjunction with any other offer or discount. Selected lines are exempt.</p>
<p>Only 10% discount available on bikes.</p>
<p>Only valid upon production of valid identification in-store or use of discount code online.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation and transfers? We’ve got you covered. Book your holiday online or give us a call. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
